This paper deals with the secure preservation of historical records of system states, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). It also involves the use of data structures and distributed systems, which are topics covered in computer science categories such as data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), distributed computing (cs.DC), software engineering (cs.SE), and databases (cs.DB).
